Category Landscape and Pricing Pack Architecture

Background

As in the current slow growth climate, many categories are driving growth primarily through price/mix as volume grows slowly or even declines. However taking an annual price raise is not so easy, with consumer transparency into market prices, cost cutting, and commodity shifts. While, even simple, sustainable innovation has always served as a means to drive healthy premiums across CPG categories.

  • market share 来看，大家的分布基本平衡

  • 善存一个distribution能卖出去更多的sales revenue意味着更高的brand awareness。
  • 不考虑price 的因素，这一awareness与其他品牌的差异更大。

  • 全品类百分之七十五的销售额来自于150元以内的产品。
  • 全品类百分之八十的销售额来自于200元以内的产品。
  • 善存定位在中端产品。

  • 善存在老年人市场比较强势(88%)，几乎没有竞争对手
  • 百分之42的Coated Tablets市场被善存占据
  • 39%的general drugform被善存占据，以及35%的western medicine
